"content": "<h2>The pen as an implement for writing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:1\">ISA 8:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:13\">3JN 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>By extension, refering to what is written</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:8\">JER 8:8</a></strong> <em>This means that what they wrote was untrue.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:18\">MAT 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:17\">LUK 16:17</a></p>\n<h2>Used symbolically</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:1\">PSA 45:1</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Sharpened with a penknife</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:23\">JER 36:23</a></p>",
